Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西弄起来还挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这样 才能成为优秀的傀儡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想你到底打算宅多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在制作新的傀儡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组装超复杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有宅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了备战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连木叶都变成了那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再发生什么也不足为奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 木叶是我们的盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法置之度外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要重建彻底摧毁的村子可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是填补空缺的火影之位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是组织上 还是精神上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为木叶支柱的火影如今不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了火影 他们能从晓带来的创伤中重振吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那里有他在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对于村子而言 你不过是令人恐惧的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要离开我们 加入正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会徒增痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层都是一些丝毫不顾及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民大都对你抱有恐惧心理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可只是空等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更剧烈的痛苦将席卷而至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有努力 靠自己解开这个枷锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不逃入只身一人的孤单之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 终有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像那家伙一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和砂隐的共同任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小事我们去不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在砂隐和我们的边境引发的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论委托哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免发生口角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就以同盟国的身份携手行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是最佳方案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是能轻松一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不过是木叶遇袭后结成的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始不可能诸事顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为修复关系的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这次任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真睿智
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连这些事都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么 到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这辈子都不会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是村子间 国家间的大人物们考虑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至于用这种语气来说嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然身为同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家融洽相处才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 闲谈到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要赶往汇合地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 到底谁会最先抵达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家比比看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 耍赖皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇合地点应该就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会迟到 肯定不是什么好人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 一提到砂隐那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是看不透他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是他们本来就很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真心同木叶修好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不应该迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迟到了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会和这家伙一起合作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我爱罗 时间刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是来早了些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的稍微晚了些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来没了杀气 变亲和了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你到底打算干吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是打个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔个石头什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能伤到他嘛 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那两位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人竟然会使出绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等恐怖的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没那么容易被认同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那帮家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天京剧王子和铁扇公主没一起出动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勘九郎和手鞠才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在所属正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的部下亚欧吉和克罗比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是亚欧吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是克罗比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这次任务的队长 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是鸣人 小樱和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是些不成熟的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗班从山的西侧出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们第七班则从东侧出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时进攻山顶的山贼据点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始时间为子时 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不用等那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区山贼轻松就能搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是山贼 他们也是叛忍集团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且据说其中也有中忍级别的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别因为你 让我们几个都陷入危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白作战方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事想事先打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我爱罗那家伙鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长们之间也会有需要商讨的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙竟然是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真臭屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有跟踪者的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不出乱子最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总得先跟你们打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经有谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被村里的上层疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会给你们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶和砂隐一起完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加深感情 这才是任务的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题越多羁绊也就越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 鸣人 小樱 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次可别迟到了 我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他会自愿加入正规部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们的任务也减轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层们都相当高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我们的酬劳也会提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的首级就归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说我爱罗大人已经有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之…绝对防御
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数忍者命丧于此也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一切顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层都是一些丝毫不顾及你感受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民大都也对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定向前迈进了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能在这此停留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底打算跟到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是写轮眼卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为气息隐藏得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不用顾忌继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不打算阻挠同盟国的忍者执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我们视为本次任务的监察者也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监察者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是监视者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗地观察任务的执行情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么监察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却戴着面具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人信不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没被信任的恐怕是我爱罗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人的力量对于我们砂隐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 正因为是自家人才更具威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人的术 你们也见识过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不应该存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算除掉我爱罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 对方还有暗杀部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对木叶而言不见得是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为其他村子的一个强大兵器将会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分 竟然将同村里的忍者给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人对于两方村子来说都是威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不该存在于世的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是村子的危险道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他们而言 是要被抹杀的过去遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是不得不这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且我明白那就是最痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就像不被需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我到底为何存在 为何而活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人绝不能活在这个世上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让他过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在砂隐 也该有能理解我爱罗的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无法接受我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过可别把我们跟你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本就是个毫不在意生命的杀人机器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个只会享受杀戮的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么容易就中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 我们的任务就简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡水遁.妖雨之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时…我爱罗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是对我们这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 怎么能抛弃同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂子吸收了凝聚查克拉的水 行动变得迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结合也变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的忍术已经被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡…鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究只是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真身只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不止一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔下您逃走 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同我爱罗大人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然被这些废物给…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上层真是小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀我 战斗力还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你们这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽耍酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我们这边的那帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本也被降服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,添麻烦的是这些家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也是砂隐的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 继续我们的任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要从这里开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这细微的羁绊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为被他人需要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是作为让人畏惧的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是作为砂隐的风影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与村里的同伴们联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了众人的认可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了成为风影的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从那家伙身上学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过逐渐加深跟同伴的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此找回了原来的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子有他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都重视同伴以及同伴间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是他和他所珍视的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也一定能够挺过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还会变得更加成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次…能再说一次刚才你们说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔下您逃跑 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前那句…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经浪费了这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没抓到小小的鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过事态比预想得复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只凭我们医疗班 人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到之后的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得不择手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 失控
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 绝对不会让你逃掉的
